      "rationale": "QoIs (construct stiffness, yield force, force at 40 mm displacement) are the clinically and regulatorily relevant performance metrics for pedicle screw constructs under ASTM F1717. These QoIs directly inform the 510(k) substantial equivalence determination and are the quantities used by FDA reviewers to assess biomechanical performance. Relevance confirmed by FDA guidance document and published literature.",
